Comparision with the Fragmentation Distribution from
40-Ar+181-Ta Reaction.
The Speg Spectrometer.
The Tof Start Signal was Provided by a Parallel Plate
Avalanche Counter, Which was Located at the Focal
Plane.
The Focal Plane Detector was Composed of a Bragg
Detector and Two Ionization Chambers, Which Could Give
The Energy, Range and Del`Ta E Information.
.The Veto Detector was a Plastic Scintillator
Detector.
.The Ganil Cyclotrons.
